sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(225, 245, 255) Fleet Customer
        participant User as Fleet Customer (Browser)
    end
    box rgb(230, 126, 34) Spryker
        participant Yves as Yves Storefront
        participant OAuth as OAuth / Auth (Zed)
        participant Strategy as CiamOauthCustomerAuthenticationStrategyPlugin (custom)
        participant Company as Customer / Company / CompanyRole
    end
    box rgb(149, 165, 166) External
        participant CIAM as CIAM (My Scania)
    end

    Note over User: No Spryker-native login — SSO only
    User->>Yves: Access shop (unauthenticated)
    Yves->>CIAM: Redirect to CIAM login [protocol TBD]
    User->>CIAM: Authenticate
    CIAM-->>Yves: Callback: token + profile<br/>(name, email, company, country, roles, products)
    Yves->>OAuth: Process SSO callback
    OAuth->>Strategy: Resolve/create CustomerTransfer
    Strategy->>Company: Find customer by email
    alt Customer does not exist
        Strategy->>Company: Create customer + company relation
        Strategy->>Company: Map CIAM roles -> Spryker Company Roles (ACL)
        Note over Strategy,Company: POC: on failure throw exception (no graceful handling)
    else Customer exists
        Strategy->>Company: Load company context + roles
    end
    Company-->>Strategy: CustomerTransfer (with company + roles)
    Strategy-->>OAuth: Authenticated customer
    OAuth-->>Yves: Session established
    Yves-->>User: Logged in — redirect to asset selection
